data.description: Awesome Ranch, Modern Farmhouse Style Home For Sale on Over 1.1 acres *Home Buyers- Buy this home with $0 down, with our preferred lender at NEXA Mortgage, plus an additional $3500 cash credit towards closing costs! For more info, call/ text The Walters Team directly. Beautifully updated, one level living on a private, tree lined 1.12 acre lot. 4 spacious bedrooms, luxury bathrooms and chef's kitchen with high- end counter tops and appliances. Perfect home for first time buyers, or those looking to downsize. This home comes with a free home warranty, and a $5000 savings guarantee for all VIP Buyers. For more information on these free buyer benefits, or to schedule a private tour, call or text and start packing!
